{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idefe82dbb-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s6524"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"6524"},"text":"§ 6524.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Organically produced food","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In the case of a food certified under the national organic program established under the Organic Foods Production Act of 1990 (","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s6501"},"text":"7 U.S.C. 6501","children":[],"tail":" et seq.), the certification shall be considered sufficient to make a claim regarding the absence of bioengineering in the food, such as “not bioengineered”, “non-GMO”, or another similar claim."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idefe82dbc-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/216/s2"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–216, § 2","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2016-07-29"},"text":"July 29, 2016","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/130/838"},"text":"130 Stat. 838","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idefe82dbd-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idefe82dbe-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idefe82dbf-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Organic Foods Production Act of 1990, referred to in text, is title XXI of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/624"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–624","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1990-11-28"},"text":"Nov. 28, 1990","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/104/3935"},"text":"104 Stat. 3935","children":[],"tail":", which is classified generally to this chapter. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s6501"},"text":"section 6501 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"idefe82dc0-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section was enacted as part of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/216"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–216","children":[],"tail":", and not as part of the Organic Foods Production Act of 1990 which comprises this chapter."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
